file.name: nullable-object.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: "1.0.0"
  title: "Sample"
paths:
  /user:
    get:
      responses:
        "200":
          description: "sample"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  user:
                    nullable: true
                    anyOf:
                    - $ref: '#/components/schemas/User'
components:
  schemas:
    User:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
